# Cyber Foundation Website Development Rules

## Deployment Workflow

### 强制流程
1. **测试服优先** - 所有更改必须先在测试服预览验证
2. **确认后发布** - 测试服OK后再用 `npx vercel --prod` 发布公网
3. **记录变更** - 重要更新需同步更新知识库

### URLs
- **公网**: https://cyber-foundation-sigma.vercel.app
- **测试服**: https://cyber-foundation-{hash}.vercel.app (push 自动生成)

## Design System

### Colors
- 背景: `#000000` (black-deep), `#0A0A0A` (black-soft)
- 文字: `#E8E8E8` (bright), `#C0C0C0` (metal), `#8A8A8A` (muted)

### Components
- `.glass-card` - 玻璃态卡片
- `.liquid-glass` - 玻璃按钮
- `.liquid-glass-pulse` - 脉冲动画按钮
- `.text-gradient-silver` - 银色渐变文字
- `.text-glow` - 发光文字

### Animations
- 使用 Framer Motion
- 进场动画: `whileInView` + `viewport={{ once: true }}`
- 悬停: `whileHover`, `whileTap`

## File Structure
```
cyber-foundation/
├── app/          # Next.js App Router pages
├── components/   # React components
├── lib/          # Constants, utils
└── public/       # Static assets
```

## Data
- 所有页面数据在 `lib/constants.ts`
- 包含: societyInfo, navLinks, socialLinks, aiSection, sciFiSection, committeeMembers, activities, projects
